ce:section.ce:para:
This paper utilizes the PDF to process voltage-capacity data. Zhang et al. [33] verified that the PDF and the capacity increment method are equally effective. Processing the voltage-capacity data with a probability distribution does not require prior adjustment and avoids the occurrence of
d V = 0
. The specific steps are as follows:
Step 1: Plot the voltage-capacity curve during the battery charge and discharge process;
Step 2: Use the Ksdensity function in MATLAB software to process the voltage-capacity curve to obtain the PDF curve;
Step 3: Translate the flat part of the capacity-voltage curve into peaks in the PDF curve, and evaluate the battery's SOH based on changes in the peaks.
